s I’ve ever seen.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe Lidl Grillmeister Gas Pizza Oven, which is already available in stores, allows you to cook your own crispy pizzas and baguettes - and eat them straight from the oven. It claims to reach 400 degrees in just 15 minutes and even comes with an integrated thermometer so you can ensure your dough is cooked to perfection.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003ePlus, with a handy viewing window and double-walled housing for optimal heat distribution, you can relax knowing your pizza is in good hands. The stone itself is 12” wide, meaning it will produce delicious, large pizzas. The pizza stone is also made from cordierite, a moisture-absorbing material that results in extra-crispy pizzas.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe oven comes with a 1m gas bottle connection hose and is suitable for five and 11kg gas bottles. It is suitable for propane gas and comes with a three year warranty.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv data-hydrate=\"true\" id=\"slice-container-newsletterForm-articleInbodyContent-2HYjSLdZbWuZPGcq5HECUM\"\u003e\u003csection\u003e\u003cp\u003eSign up to our newsletter for style and decor inspiration, house makeovers, project advice and more.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cfigure data-bordeaux-image-check=\"\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/8CLzm2B33WtE57hsE28UvK-1920-80.png.webp 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/8CLzm2B33WtE57hsE28UvK-1600-80.png.webp 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/8CLzm2B33WtE57hsE28UvK-1280-80.png.webp 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/8CLzm2B33WtE57hsE28UvK-1024-80.png.webp 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/8CLzm2B33WtE57hsE28UvK-768-80.png.webp 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/8CLzm2B33WtE57hsE28UvK-415-80.png.webp 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/8CLzm2B33WtE57hsE28UvK-360-80.png.webp 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/8CLzm2B33WtE57hsE28UvK-320-80.png.